OL,7,FThe number of children being admitted
OL,8,Fto acute hospital wards due to
OL,9,Fconcerns over their mental health has
OL,10,Fincreased by almost two-thirds in a
OL,11,Fdecade, according to a study.
OL,13,FThe rise was particularly high in
OL,14,Fgirls aged 11 to 15, with the analysis
OL,15,Falso highlighting "steep relative
OL,16,Fincreases" among children aged five to
OL,17,F10 and "striking rates of self-harm in
OL,18,Ffemales".
