OL,4,Cadmitted to acute wards for mental
OL,5,Chealth issues
OL,7,FResearchers found that between 2012
OL,8,Fand 2022, annual admissions for mental
OL,9,Fhealth concerns increased by 65%, from
OL,10,F24,198 to 39,925.
OL,12,FDr Lee Hudson, of UCL Great Ormond
OL,13,FStreet Institute of Child Health and
OL,14,FGreat Ormond Street Hospital, said:
OL,15,F"Over the past decade, we've observed
OL,16,Fa significant rise in mental health
OL,17,Fadmissions among children and young
OL,18,Fpeople to acute medical wards.
