OL,7,F"Although there has been attention
OL,8,Fpaid to increased referrals to
OL,9,Fcommunity mental health services and
OL,10,Finpatient mental health settings,
OL,11,Fadmissions to general acute medical
OL,12,Fsettings feels like a piece of the
OL,13,Fjigsaw missing in the story."
OL,15,FThe rise in admissions was
OL,16,F"particularly steep" in girls aged 11
OL,17,Fto 15, researchers said, climbing from
OL,18,F9,901 to 19,349, an increase of 112.8%.
