OL,7,FReacting to the study, Dr Karen
OL,8,FStreet, officer for mental health at
OL,9,Fthe Royal College of Paediatrics and
OL,10,FChild Health, said: "A 65% increase in
OL,11,Fmental health admissions further
OL,12,Fevidences the alarming deterioration
OL,13,Fin the mental health and wellbeing of
OL,14,Four children and young people."
OL,16,FShe also called for more to be done to
OL,17,Funderstand what is causing the
OL,18,Fincrease in mental health admissions.
