OL,7,F"We know that the pandemic had a
OL,8,Fprofound impact on children and young
OL,9,Fpeople," Dr Street added.
OL,11,F"Yet, rates of worsening mental health
OL,12,Famong this cohort were also reported
OL,13,Fin 2012, indicating that Covid-19 is
OL,14,Fnot the sole factor.
OL,16,F"More must be done to find out and
OL,17,Funderstand the core drivers for this
OL,18,Funparalleled increase to truly design
OL,19,Fa service which works for our young
OL,20,Fpeople."
